		<div id="comment_body_64534153"><p>I have already mentioned that, see <a href="https://slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23349631&amp;cid=64532579" title="slashdot.org">https://slashdot.org/comments....</a> [slashdot.org] (search for "Bill Gates").</p><p>Pollution is not a zero sum game. You can produce stuff more or less efficient. C.f., the pollution in Western Europe and the East Bloc during the Cold war.</p><p>Yes, and there is only one feasible way to prevent disaster. Fewer humans. Again, see the post I linked to above.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64534153">

